programme.title: Halalkan Hati Yang Ku Curi S1 Ep14
programme.desc: Kedua-dua Delisha dan Faiq melalui detik-detik kesusahan dan cabaran hidup. Mereka terpaksa membeli baju murah, tidur di hotel bajet, makan di warung. Sekarang, Faiq semakin tahu erti kesusahan, isterinya masih ada perasaan ego. Dia terus berlagak seperti orang berkemampuan. Dari jauh Delisha ternampak Zainal bersama Salima, Delisha ingin mendapatkan mereka, mungkin mereka tahu di mana Nendanya tetapi tidak disetujui Faiq. Dari situ mereka ke pejabat Nendanya, tiba di sana pejabat itu bukan lagi milik Nendanya dan mereka juga tidak dilayan di situ. Manakala Salima telah pun selesai majlis pertunangan mereka. Sikap Zainal yang terus berada di rumah Salima, membuatkan ibu Salima terpaksa berterus terang meminta Zainal pulang dahulu. Tingkah laku Zainal tidak sukai dan disenangi ibu Salima. Dalam pada itu, Salima terus dengan ego dan kerap bersama Zainal ke butik untuk mempersiapkan perkahwinan mereka.

Mizan menunjukkan hubungan dia dengan Hani mesra. Hani secara ikhlas juga menunjukkan mesranya mereka berdua. Walau pun begitu mereka tidak sempat bersama sebagai suami isteri, bererti sejak mereka berkahwin masih berkeadaan sedemikian kerana di Kuala Lumpur pun mereka tinggal di bilik berasingan. Kesempatan Mizan dapat berbual ringkas dengan Hani, Mizan memberi amaran kepada Hani supaya sentiasa menunjukkanhubungan mereka kepada kedua-dua ibu bapa sebagai tidak ada masalah apa-apa pun. Hani akur, Kebetulan anak Sheila tidak sihat membuatkan semasa Mizan hendak pulang ke Kuala Lumpur, Hani tidak turut serta. Semasa Mizan hendak pulang, kedua-dua mereka "beraksi", pura-pura baik dan mesra kerana ibu dan bapa mereka ada bersama. Sheila kini bukan sahaja berterima kasih kepada Sheila tetapi dia juga menceritakan Nizam seorang yang baik, sanggup menerimanya. Dia juga menanti Nizam dengan penuh mengharap menerimanya. Selain itu menyatakan ibu dan bapanya mungkin akan bertambah marah apabila dapat tahu dia telah melahirkan anak. Mizan selepas tiba di Kuala Lumpur kelihatan kurang ceria dan menjadi kehairanan kepada Zul.

programme.desc: Nasib baik sekuriti kondo bantu Suzan. Disebabkan tak nak Aidid ambil tindakan, Sherry ketemu Haryati dan Aidid lalu minta selesaikan hal ni. Aidid janji lepaskan Juliana asalkan Juliana tak muncul lagi depan Aidid dan Suzan. Haryati yang malu, bawa diri lalu kenal dengan sorang ahli NGO bernama Ustazah Ummi Fikrah. Haryati rasa Ummi Fikrah pelik. Suatu malam, Haryati sakit. Lalu Ummi Fikrah bawa Haryati balik rumahnya dan Haryati selesa dan nak tinggal situ. Sebab risau juga, Aidid dan Suzan muncul cari Haryati di rumah Ummi Fikrah. Haryati nampak tak senang.

programme.title: Pinggan Tak Retak Nasi Tak Dingin Ep10
programme.desc: Memaparkan Sheila sangat mengharapkan Hani dapat berhubung dengan Nizam kerana Hani sahaja yang akan dilayan panggilan. Hani menelefon Nizam semata-mata kerana harapan Sheila, merayu dia pulang. Sheila berharap dia dapat meminta maaf akibat kesalahannya. Kesempatan Hani berbual, Nizam sering memujuk Hani, menyuarakan segala perasaan dan janji mereka dahulu. Malahan Mizan dengan berkeras hati menyatakan cintanya hanya Hani, bagi Sheila dia tidak sesekali akan memaafkannya. Apabila Hani menyatakan kesetiaan hanyalah kepada suaminya. Nizam sekali lagi bertegas yang dia akan menentukan Mizan tidak menyentuhnya. Hani walau pun seperti berbelah bagi, tetapi dia seorang yang cekal dan tetap taat kepada suaminya. Di sebelah malamnya, Hani terbawa-bawa bagaimana kisah mereka berdua bercinta dahulu. Malahan di satu taman, pernah mereka sama-sama meletakkan "kunci cinta" mereka sebagai janji seia sekata. Suraya masih dengan rakan lelaki yang cuba mencari kerja untuk dia menjadi "modelling". Apa pun melalui jalan pintas Suraya juga bersetuju menjadi pelacur berkelas melalui seorang ahli perniagaan berbangsa Cina. Mizan tidak berapa sihat, kebetulan Hani telah pulang ke rumah. Hani menjagai Mizan dengan sebaiknya. Mizan juga mahukan Hani memanggil dirinya "abang", yang menjadi Hani terasa berlainan. Mereka juga mula keluar bersekali bersantai.

programme.title: Syurgaku Tak Sempurna S1 Ep2
programme.desc: Tengku Kamal semakin risau dengan sikap anaknya.Tengku Zaharah mula mengatur rancangan dengan memperkenalkan anak anak rakannya kepada Tengku Zarif.Makin hari Tengku Zarif sedar yang tiada gunanya dia terus menyesali nasib diri dan meratap hanya kerana putus cinta dengan Suzanna.Dia nekad kembali bangun dan berjumpa dengan Tengku Kamal untuk kembali menguruskan empayer perniagaan mereka.Tengku Kamal sangat gembira dengan perubahan positif dari Tengku Zarif.Zalia pula takut untuk pulang ke kampung dan dia mencari peluang pekerjaan lain dan diterima bekerja di restoran Zairul.Tengku Zaharah masih cuba untuk menjodohkan anaknya dengan anak teman baiknya yang baru pulang dari overseas iaitu Tengku Fariena.Tengku Zarif dan Tengku Fariena merupakan sahabat karib sejak dari kecil lagi.

programme.title: Disebalik Wajah S1 Ep14
programme.desc: Perasaan cemburu dan syak wasangka membuatkan Amir dan Nadia selalu bergaduh. Ryan tidak terputus-putus mengingatkan Amir untuk berhati hati dengan Nadia kerana apa yang pernah dilakukannya sebelum itu. Red dan Nadia bersetuju untuk mengurangkan pertemuan mereka supaya Nadia dapat memulihkan hubungan dengan suaminya. Di suatu hari, ketika Amir tertidur, Nadia terdengar Amir menyebut nama Syakila, dan Nadia mula tertanya-tanya, siapa Syakila.

programme.title: MAMA
programme.desc: Kisah bermula pada hari lahir ke-15 Alya (Bella Dowanna) yang disambut setiap tahun bersama mamanya, Aini (Nabila Huda). Setelah kematian suami ketika Alya berusia lapan tahun, Aini berusaha keras setiap hari untuk memberikan kehidupan yang lebih baik untuk untuk anaknya.

programme.title: Disebalik Wajah S1 Ep2
programme.desc: Nadia dibawa pulang ke rumah dan Amir memberitahunya mereka memang saling mencintai, tetapi Nadia keliru kerana seperti ada 'suara' yang bermain dalam fikirannya mengatakan Amir adalah musuh. Tidak lama kemudian, suspek kes tembak Amir ditahan polis.

programme.title: The Hoarder
programme.desc: Ella dipaksa bekerja dengan sekumpulan orang asing yang menakutkan selepas terperangkap di kemudahan penyimpanan bawah tanah di mana dia mendapati dirinya diburu oleh pembunuh yang tidak dikenali.

programme.title: Seekers Underground Ep56
programme.desc: Seekers kembali dengan nama baru Seekers Underground. Dengan teknologi baru serta tinjaun ke lokasi yang belum pernah diterokai

programme.title: Chikaro
programme.desc: Mengisahkan seorang gadis kampung naif yang datang ke bandar untuk mencari pekerjaan di sebuah pejabat dan di situ dia telah bertemu dengan bekas mat rempit yang telah jatuh cinta pada pandangan pertama. Dia berusaha untuk menolong gadis itu sesuaikan diri dengan gaya hidup bandar dan akhirnya gadis kampung itu juga telah jatuh cinta kepadanya. Walaubagaimanapun kerana sifatnya yang matang, ramai wanita mencemburuinya.

programme.title: Syurgaku Tak Sempurna S1 Ep10
programme.desc: Zalia makin bertambah sedih dan meminta kebenaran Tengku Zarif untuk pulang ke kampung bersama Tengku Zaeem untuk bertemu ayahnya.Zalia menceritakan pada ayahnya dia yakin pil yang diberi oleh Tengku Zaharah itu yang menyebabkan dia gugur.Zahid nasihatkan Zalia supaya jangan menuduh yang bukan-bukan.Dalam hati Zahid mula cemburu kerana Zalia terlalu sayangkan anaknya dan seolah-olah tidak memperdulikan dia yang selama ini membesarkan Zalia tanpa seorang ibu di sisi.Takdir menentukan umur Tengku Zaeem tidak panjang,dia tewas di tangan Zahid .Zahid hanya menyaksikan dia lemas dan menjerut leher Tengku Zaeem tanpa ada perasaan belas di hati akibat dendam lama......Tengku Zaharah mengamuk dan makin benci pada Zalia!

programme.title: London Has Fallen
programme.desc: Apabila Yeon Joon mengetahui bahawa Eun Su hanya menganggapnya sebagai abangnya, hen berasa sangat kecewa. Sementara itu, Kim Ho Ran menjalankan ujian DNA dengan rambut Eun Su dan Woo Joo.

programme.title: Seekers Underground Ep56
programme.desc: Seekers kembali dengan nama baru Seekers Underground. Dengan teknologi baru serta tinjaun ke lokasi yang belum pernah diterokai

programme.title: Azem 2
programme.desc: Beberapa orang membawa seorang gadis yang dirasuk teruk dengan kotak kayu berkunci untuk menyembuhkannya.

programme.title: Wolf Warrior II
programme.desc: TBC

programme.title: Tu Dia S1 Ep28
programme.desc: Saksikan gelagat hos anda Aliff Satar, Farish Aziz & Zoey Rahman dalam Tu Dia! Pelbagai segmen menarik bakal menghiburkan malam anda.

programme.title: Kembang Kantil
programme.desc: Untuk menghadiri persembahan teater Alisa (Bella Ireland) pergi ke rumah abangnya Anton (Fadika Royandi) dan isterinya Santi (Nafa Urbach). Di rumah Alisa bertemu Tania (Richelle Georgette Skonicki), anak angkat Anton dan Siska.

programme.title: You Saka..Pergi Jauh-jauh S1 Ep1
programme.desc: Episod Pertama cereka komedi seram disusuli dengan kepercayaan khurafat ini berkisar kepada personaliti Nia. Nia sebagai setiausaha syarikat milik seorang Datin Salina yang amat menyukainya hingga bercadang untuk dijodohkan kepada anak lelakinya. Ibu Nia dikampung, sedang sakit dijagai oleh Roslan, bapa saudaranya (Pak Lang). Nia mempercayai dia wajar menyeru puteri yang sesekali Nia akan lakukan bertujuan melindunginya dan juga sebagai amalan turun temurunnya selama ini. Jika tidak dilakukan, saka berbentuk syaitan akan menggangguinya. Ada sebab-sebab bahawa ibunya memiliki saka dan kematiannya bererti saka itu cuba mempengaruhi warisnya iaitu Nia. Nia tinggal dengan Shasa dan sepupu Shasa iaitu, Adrus adalah 'boy friend' Nia. Adrus sedang menceburi kerjaya dalam bidang paranormal, merupakan anak Ibrahim seorang bomoh. Ketika ibu Nia meninggal dunia dia belum ketahui. Sementara itu, semasa pengembumian ibunya berlaku juga kekecuhan iaitu muncul lembaga putih (berbentuk manusia - wanita). Selain dari itu, sesekali saka Gelam berbentuk syaitan (hitam jalur hijau) mengganggui Nia, 'boy friend'nya dan pernah bersama lembaga putih mengganggui bomoh Ibrahim.

programme.title: Danur2: Maddah
programme.desc: Seorang gadis yang mempunyai 3 rakan hantu kini tinggal bersama kakaknya yang semakin malu dengan keupayaan gadis itu untuk melihat hantu.

programme.title: Santau Merasuk Ep6
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Echa kembali tenang setelah dia diserang histeria sekolah. Halim bersama Maya bergegas pulang bila mendapat panggilan dari Nina. Halim sempat telefon Mat minta bantuan. Nina yang sudah tidak tahan apa yang berlaku, mahu berpindah dari situ. Tetapi berjaya dipujuk Maya dengan beberapa cadangannya. Halim memanggil beberapa orang surau untuk memulihkan rumahnya.

programme.title: Tu Dia S1 Ep29
programme.desc: Saksikan gelagat hos anda Aliff Satar, Farish Aziz & Zoey Rahman dalam Tu Dia! Pelbagai segmen menarik bakal menghiburkan malam anda.

programme.title: Disebalik Wajah S1 Ep15
programme.desc: Pihak polis telah menjumpai mayat yang mereka syaki adalah Elisa. Nadia mula bertanya kepada Amir jika dia mengenali sesiapa bernama Syakila. Amir cuba menukar topik dengan bertanya terus tentang hubungan Nadia dengan Red. Sementara itu, Red yang semakin resah dengan kehilangan Elisa mula ketepikan tugas kerjanya. Di rumah Puan Sri Zabedah, Red bertemu dengan Amir kerana dia baru dapat klu yang mengatakan Nadia adalah seseorang yang tidak boleh dipercayai.

programme.title: Danur2: Maddah

programme.title: Dendam Sarakit S1 Ep13
programme.desc: Episod terakhir yang mengisahkan Pak Bado dijumpai mati dibunuh. Disebabkan ini, Ramdi telah memberitahu Ustaz Hambali apa yang berlaku kepada Sarakit yang dirogol dan kemudiannya dibunuh Pak Bado. Ustaz Hambali telah berusaha menyelesaikan masalah yang dihadapi dengan memulihkan semangat Rafiq dan menghalau jin Sarakit dari badan Dina. Akibatnya Dina telah meninggal dunia. Dengan bantuan orang-orang kampung, mereka berjaya berjumpa kubur Sarakit dan Rafiq redha dengan apa yang berlaku terhadap Sarakit. Rafiq meninggalkan kampung dan Ramdi kemudiannya menjadi buta apabila terjatuh mencederakan matanya.

programme.title: Syurgaku Tak Sempurna S1 Ep11
programme.desc: Tengku Zarif kasihan melihat Zalia yang hidup tak ubah seperti mayat hidup kerana asyik menyalahkan diri sendiri atas kematian anaknya.Zalia minta diceraikan tetapi tidak mudah bagi Tengku ZARIF.Dia membawa Zalia bercuti dan Zalia sarankan mereka mengambil anak angkat tapi masih terlalu awal bagi Tengku Zarif.Adik Tengku Zarif iaitu Zahir baru pulang dari overseas dan marah dengan apa yang berlaku selepas Tengku Zaharah ceritakan semuanya .Zahir cuba 'tackle' Tengku Fariena tapi ditentang oleh Tengku Zaharah kerana tidak mahu Zahir kacau 'plannya'.Zahir bengang!

programme.title: Ular
programme.desc: Sekumpulan pemenang cabutan bertuah memenangi percutian impian di resort pulau yang kelihatan indah, hanya untuk mendapati diri mereka terperangkap di pulau yang dipenuhi ular maut.

programme.title: Tu Dia S1 Ep29
programme.desc: Saksikan gelagat hos anda Aliff Satar, Farish Aziz & Zoey Rahman dalam Tu Dia! Pelbagai segmen menarik bakal menghiburkan malam anda.

programme.title: MAMA
programme.desc: Kisah bermula pada hari lahir ke-15 Alya (Bella Dowanna) yang disambut setiap tahun bersama mamanya, Aini (Nabila Huda). Setelah kematian suami ketika Alya berusia lapan tahun, Aini berusaha keras setiap hari untuk memberikan kehidupan yang lebih baik untuk untuk anaknya.

programme.title: Terror Newspaper Ep1
programme.desc: Kehidupan universiti Shizuru Onoda bertukar menjadi mimpi ngeri apabila dia menerima Akhbar Keganasan, kerana insiden dari akhbar itu berlaku satu demi satu. Membaca kertas sekali setiap hari juga memendekkan jangka hayat sebanyak 100 hari. Bagaimanakah Shizuru boleh terselamat daripada kejadian yang amat menakutkan ini?

programme.title: Bodyguard S1 Ep14
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Farish sebagai bodyguard pelakon Kasandra menjumpai telefon tangan kedua yang sealu digunakan oleh Mazlan untuk mengugut Kasandra. Farish memaklumkan kepada Kasandra supaya memecat Mazlan. Dalam kes berasingan, Nasha mengambil Bakri seorang bodyguard baru untuk menggantikan Rahul, pada masa yang sama dapat membantu Ryan menyelesaikan kes Haris dan Anuar. Ryan mendapati lokasi kegiatan haram Samad telah berpindah ke lokasi baru. Dia menjalankan menjual dadah. Sementara itu, Hakim dan Yasmin yang lari dari rumah. Semasa berkelah, Hakim telah memukul pengurus pusat perkelahan dan Yasmin kerana marah dengan mereka. Perhubungan Farish dengan Nasha semakin erat setelah Farish menghadiahkan bunga kepadanya.

programme.title: 4bia
programme.desc: Empat kisah seram berkisar tentang mangsa kemalangan, remaja yang dibuli, cerita hantu dan puteri yang telah meninggal dunia

programme.title: Jejaka Perasan
programme.desc: Dolah dan Dolit, masing-masing telah dihalau dari rumah oleh ibu dan isteri kerana malas bekerja dan gemar bermain judi kuda. Mereka pun menyewa bilik di rumah Pak Wok. Pak Wok tinggal bersama anaknya Rizan yang sedang bercinta dengan Amir. Mereka ditawarkan bekerja sebagai tukang cuci oleh Dato Kamarul kerana telah membantu membaiki kereta anaknya, Dora. Mulalah tersebar cerita bahawa mereka merupakan pegawai tetapi sebenarnya tidak.

programme.title: Si Jantung Hati
programme.desc: Dua adik beradik, Do dan Re, keluar menggembara untuk mencari harta pusaka kepunyaan ayah mereka yang telah lama disembunyikan. Sebelum itu, mereka perlu mencari sahabat lama ayah mereka yang mempunyai petunjuk lokasi harta itu. Tetapi sesuatu terjadi apabila musuh lama muncul kembali untuk mengambil harta pusaka itu kerana yakin bahawa itu miliknya yang telah dicuri ayah mereka bertahun-tahun dahulu.

programme.title: Pak Tam Duda
programme.desc: Dihormati oleh orang-orang kampung kerana baik-hati dan pemurah, Pak Tam ialah seorang duda dan usahawan yang berjaya di kampungnya. Pada suatu hari, muncul seorang gadis dari bandar yang ingin menggoda Pak Tam demi hartanya. Gadis ini telah merancang segalanya bersama teman lelakinya. Niat jahat mereka telah dihidu budak-budak kampung yang tampil memberikan nasihat kepada Pak Tam.

programme.title: Manis Manis Sayang
programme.desc: Terkesan dengan tingkah laku Bahadom terhadapnya di khalayak ramai, Jalil membuat keputusan untuk berhenti bekerja. Namun Bahadom mempunyai rancangan lain apabila Datuk menyuruhnya untuk mencari seorang pegawai untuk dihantar ke luar negara. Kerana bencikan Jalil dan juga ingin memisahkannya dari Rosnah, Bahadom mahu menghantar Jalil ke luar negara.

programme.title: Pagar Pagar Cinta
programme.desc: Pelbagai rintangan terpaksa dihadapi Bidin dan Rosnah kerana cinta antara dua darjat. Bidin, anak orang kaya manakala Rosnah hanyalah seorang yang biasa-biasa sahaja. Ibu bapa Bidin ingin menjodohkannya dengan Rita, anak kepada kenalannya yang kaya-raya. Berbagai cara terpaksa dilakukan oleh Bidin untuk menyakinkan bahawa Rosnahlah pilihan hatinya. Berjayakah rancangan Bidin untuk melembutkan hati ibu bapanya?

programme.title: Jejaka Perasan
programme.desc: Dolah dan Dolit, masing-masing telah dihalau dari rumah oleh ibu dan isteri kerana malas bekerja dan gemar bermain judi kuda. Mereka pun menyewa bilik di rumah Pak Wok. Pak Wok tinggal bersama anaknya Rizan yang sedang bercinta dengan Amir. Mereka ditawarkan bekerja sebagai tukang cuci oleh Dato Kamarul kerana telah membantu membaiki kereta anaknya, Dora. Mulalah tersebar cerita bahawa mereka merupakan pegawai tetapi sebenarnya tidak.

programme.title: Penyamun Tarbus
programme.desc: Tuan Said seorang yang kaya raya tetapi sering mengelat dari membayar cukai, menyimpan semua rekod di dalam peti besi miliknya. Malang sekali, rekod dan tarbus miliknya dicuri penyamun - untuk membalas dendam terhadap Tuan Said kerana tidak menerima mereka bekerja atas faktor umur. Tidak ingin rahsianya diketahui, diupahnya penyiasat penyendirian untuk menjejaki penyamun itu.

programme.title: Pening Pening Lalat
programme.desc: Dino berjaya melarikan diri dari sebuah penjara dan sedang berada dalam buruan polis. Berita tentangnya mendapat liputan besar dan ditawarkan wang sebanyak RM10,000 kepada sesiapa yang menangkapnya. Mengetahui tentang itu, Dino mula menyembunyikan diri. Memutuskan untuk bersembunyi di hutan, Dino bertemu Zakaria dan Aliza.

programme.title: Hantu Siang
programme.desc: Seorang kasanova yang suka menggoda gadis menerima padahnya apabila harus mengahwini mangsanya. Badul telah berjaya mendampingi lebih 17 gadis. Dia mempunyai rancangan untuk menggoda dua lagi gadis baru sebagai mangsanya. Rancangan Badul memakan diri apabila dia sendiri terpaksa menikahi mereka - cubaannya telah memerangkap dirinya sendiri.

programme.title: Bertunang
programme.desc: Darus ingin dikahwini dengan Zarinah, anak pengurus bank oleh bapa saudaranya - dia merupakan seorang yang kaya-raya. Namun, Darus melarikan diri kerana dia enggan mengahwini Zarinah dan sudah mempunyai kekasih hati. Mengetahui tujuan bapa saudaranya ingin menjodohkannya bersama anak seorang pengurus bank untuk membiayai projeknya, Darus hilang membawa diri - tetapi bapa saudaranya mempunyai rancangannya yang tersendiri.

programme.title: Si Badol
programme.desc: Perjuangan kelas pekerja digambarkan apabila kapitalisme semakin mendapat tempat di dunia. Badol, seorang penipu, menyamar menjadi orang kaya yang datang dari Sarawak lalu mengahwini Milah. Tipu helah digunakannya untuk memperdaya orang kaya. Modus operandinya adalah dengan meminjam wang yang banyak. Badol pun pergi menghilangkan diri setelah berjaya memperdaya orang kaya.

programme.title: Oh Fatimah
programme.desc: Perpisahan antara Rahmat dan Fatimah telah membawa keduanya untuk membina kehidupan baru bersama pasangan yang lebih baik. Kedua-duanya mula berkenalan dengan orang baru dan masing-masing cuba untuk menunjukkan betapa bagusnya pasangan baru mereka itu. Akan tetapi, sikap Rahmat yang mulai berubah telah mencairkan semula hati Fatimah - namun kesetiaan Rahmat perlu diuji dahulu sebelum Fatimah dapat membuat keputusan.

programme.title: Tuan Badol
programme.desc: Seorang yang sangat garang tetapi rupa-rupanya takut dengan isteri, itulah Ibrahim. Seorang Pengurus Besar, dia mempunyai seorang pembantu rumah bernama Nor. Tuan Badol jatuh cinta terhadap Nor apabila melakukan lawatan ke tanah miliknya. Pelbagai cara telah dicubanya untuk memikat Nor, seorang yang hidup serba sederhana di tanah perkampungan setinggan miliknya.

programme.title: Youngju
programme.desc: Young-Ju, barely 18 years old, works to support her younger brother after her parents died. She decides to meet the people responsible for her parents' deaths when she needs financial help.

programme.title: The Girl On A Bulldozer
programme.desc: As the girl seeks truth behind the sudden car accident of her father, anger and despair left her only one option.

programme.title: Spellbound
programme.desc: Yeo-Ri has the ability to see ghosts. When she joins Jo-Goo's magic show, he offers to help her find a way out before the ghosts can chase him out of her life.

programme.title: Unbowed
programme.desc: A math professor was not re-hired for pointing out errors in the university entrance exam. Losing the lawsuit against the university, he carries his crossbow to the judge for justice.

programme.title: Taste of Life (T) Ep843844
programme.desc: Chu-Tsai,Chao and his wife Chin-hsiu,Li have five children. Devoted all his life into developing soy sauce products, Chu-Tsai very much hopes that one of his kids can follow his footsteps and take over his business, but he also respects their own passions and aspirations. Because of their father’s invention dream, the Chao brothers’ lives are about to change… Chin-Pang,Chou used to be Chin-Hsiu’s lover, and has been Chu-Tsai’s long-time business rival. Seeing Chu-Tsai not only successfully keep the patents of soy sauce products, but also has all the support and assistance from his children, Chin-Pang, filled with bitterness, has been crushing and attacking Chu-Tsai in every way. Hsin-Ta, Chu-Tsai’s eldest son, couldn’t bear to see his father suffer, so he quit his job to take over the family business. To everyone’s surprise, Chu-Tsai discovers that Hsin-Ta is actually Chin-Pang’s son! Finding out that the enemy is actually his biological father devastated Hsin-Ta, and this also drives a wedge between Chin-pang and his son Hsiao-Ming, as he feels threatened. Chu-tsai’s second son Ying-kai has always set his goal to reach the top of his career. Vacillating between Mei-mei and Ying-hui, Ying-kai also finds himself caught in between the feud of two families; however, this opens new business opportunities for him. On the other hand, Hsin-ta fulfills Chu-tsai’s dream; but he is more confused than ever about family love and romance love… All he knows is that with the family’s support, his determination and conviction, he can build a future of his own!

programme.title: All U Need is Love
programme.desc: Ten major film companies join forces on a comedy-drama film to raise funds and create jobs for industry workers during the COVID-19 pandemic. This film features an all-star ensemble cast starring for free, with the story revolving around a group of hotel guests placed under quarantine in Hong Kong.

programme.title: Heroic Duo
programme.desc: Police officer Ken needs help to solve a grisly crime that the offender has no recollection of committing. Ken seeks out Jack, a former psychologist who is now imprisoned. Forming an uneasy truce, this unconventional duo sets out to find the man responsible. It is at this time that Ken falls into a trap set up by Jack…

programme.title: Blind War
programme.desc: Former SWAT captain Dong Gu suffers traumatic visual loss during a failed mission for which he is forced to take responsibility. He manages to get over and adapt to the situation with his daughter’s company, until his nemesis appears and puts his daughter in danger. Despite being blind, Dong Gu must fight to save his daughter.

programme.title: Mr McDreamy
programme.desc: A second generation rich man squanders his parents’ money and calls himself Mr McDreamy. When his parents finally have enough and cut him off financially, he establishes a “Mr McDreamy Training Academy” using various unconventional means to transform his four recruits into “Mr McDreamies” with hilarious results.

programme.title: A Better Tomorrow 2018
programme.desc: In this remake of John Woo's legendary heroic bloodshed movie, a former drug smuggler attempts to start his life anew and repair his relationship with his estranged brother, who is a rising star in the Police Narcotics Division.

programme.title: A Murder Erased
programme.desc: Police officer Choi is assigned to a death scene investigation where the deceased body had laid undiscovered for eight years. A prosecutor joins the investigation after Choi has identified the suspect, and finds Choi’s actions suspicious when all manner of inconsistencies come to light from his statement...

programme.title: Golden Chicken
programme.desc: Ah Kam, a life-long prostitute, gets locked inside a cash machine vestibule with a would be thief. Both discover they are ill-fated in life and Ah Kam starts telling him her life story as a prostitute, from a teenage hooker to a PR girl in an upscale club in her thirties, as well as being a strip dancer, bar girl and masseuse.

programme.title: Wolf Warrior II
programme.desc: In this action-packed sequel to the 2015 blockbuster hit, China’s deadliest Special Forces operative, Leng Feng (Wu Jing), returns into action when he crosses paths with a sadistic band of mercenaries terrorizing innocent civilians.

programme.title: Viral
programme.desc: Following the outbreak of a virus that wipes out the majority of the human population, a young woman documents her family's new life in quarantine and tries to protect her infected sister.

programme.title: Legend of Mysterious Agent
programme.desc: Female students in Baicheng are missing and killed by vampires. Exorcism trio tries to trace and hunt them down. Can Ming, a Millennium vampire, disguises as Baicheng Warlord, only to collect the blood of missing girls...

programme.title: The Sinking City Capsule Odyssey
programme.desc: A group of people living in ‘space capsules’ – large seminar rooms subdivided into small living quarters - struggle to fight for their ideal way of life in the prosperous yet divided city of Hong Kong.

programme.title: God of War
programme.desc: During the 16th century, pirates rule the Chinese coastline, pillaging the small villages and terrorizing the citizens. When maverick leader Commander Yu (martial arts legend Sammo Hung) enlists the help of a sharp young general (Vincent Zhao), they devise a plan to defeat the pirates.

programme.title: Hotel Deluxe
programme.desc: Bai Xing Hotel is a five-star luxury hotel located in Qian Dao Lake, Hang Zhou, with a service level only worthy of a four-star hotel. The head office sent Cruella Koo, a tough executive, to lead reforms for the hotel and upgrade the employees’ performance to reach the five-star level.

programme.title: A Murder Erased
programme.desc: Police officer Choi is assigned to a death scene investigation where the deceased body had laid undiscovered for eight years. A prosecutor joins the investigation after Choi has identified the suspect, and finds Choi’s actions suspicious when all manner of inconsistencies come to light from his statement...

programme.title: The Calling of a Bus Driver
programme.desc: A girl named Suki fulfills her dream of being a bus driver after breaking up with her boyfriend, who has an affair with her good friend. When Suki is invited to attend her ex-boyfriend’s wedding, she is presented with a chance for revenge – will she take it and turn her life around?

programme.title: Kung Fu Jungle
programme.desc: A vicious killer goes around challenging and killing top refined martial arts masters. When convicted killer and kung fu expert Hahou Mo hears of this, he offers to help the police capture the killer in exchange for his freedom. Can he really help?

programme.title: Golden Chicken 2
programme.desc: The sequel is set in 2046 when a 82-year-old Ah Kam stops a heartbroken young man from taking memory loss pills. To help ease his pain, Ah Kam shares her life stories from 2003, one of Hong Kong’s toughest year with SARS, including the different people she comes across and the bittersweet romance between herself and her cousin.

programme.title: The Fatal Raid
programme.desc: Twenty years after a deadly bloodbath between the Hong Kong Police and Macau gangsters, Madam Fong, the surviving team member, leads a new squad of four policewomen across borders to pursue young anarchists terrorizing Macau in a mission to protect the Hong Kong Police’s Deputy Chief Commissioner.

programme.title: In the Mood for Love
programme.desc: “In the Mood for Love” is Wong Kar-Wai’s most acclaimed feature, navigating the subtle love relationship between Chow Mo Wan and Su Li Zhen after both discover their spouses are having an affair. Tony Leung won Best Actor at the 53rd Cannes Film Festival for his leading role and was the first Hong Kong artiste to receive this honour.

programme.title: New Kung Fu Cult Master 1
programme.desc: Wu Dang Sect’s Zhang Chui Shan’s son, Zhang Wu Ji, finds himself accidentally embroiled in the fight for the Dragon Sabre. When he unwittingly learns the powerful martial arts skills from the Jiuyin scriptures, Wu Ji proceeds to help the Six Major sects fight against the corrupt government.

programme.title: Shoplifters
programme.desc: A Japanese family with lowly paid part-time jobs turns to shoplifting to make ends meet. After one shoplifting session, the father Osamu and his son come across a little girl in the cold. Osamu’s wife agrees to take her in after learning her hardships, and they seem to live happily together until an unforeseen incident reveals hidden secrets..

programme.title: Cold War
programme.desc: A hijacking of a police van occurs when the Police Commissioner is away from Hong Kong. Deputy Commissioner Lee leads a rescue operation code-named Cold War. Fellow Deputy Commissioner Sean moves to take control from Lee as he thinks Lee is emotionally affected by his son being held hostage, but the efforts end up threatening both their reputation.

programme.title: Aberdeen
programme.desc: The Cheng family embodies a microcosm of Hong Kong, with its contradictions between tradition and modernity, superstition and materialism, family and individual. The movie reveals troubled characters dealing with their own issues in the city, from the eldest, Taoist priest patriarch Dong; to the youngest, the bullied elementary schooler Chloe.

programme.title: Distinction
programme.desc: A music teacher in a special needs school, an underachiever from an elite school, and a rebellious teenager with a handicapped brother take part in a campus musical for various reasons. Little did they know that this turns out to be a journey of self-discovery.

programme.title: Princess & 7 Kung Fu Masters
programme.desc: Seven Kung Fu masters live in Lucky Town, the only safe residing place in northeast China. When warlord Lam refuses to side with the Japanese, an agent is assigned to take over his army and kill his daughter using ninjutsu. Lam’s daughter escapes and seeks help from the seven masters, who finally defeat the enemy and save the warlord!

programme.title: Big Brother
programme.desc: Henry Chen, a former soldier, is recruited for his toughest mission yet - teaching a class of teen delinquents. As he kicks his way into their school and home lives, it becomes clear that his unconventional teaching style might be just what they need.

programme.title: You are the One
programme.desc: A talented rogue trader experiences a 180-degree change in life when he encounters a girl who does not believe good things will happen to her. Will they fall in love? It seems like a Cinderella’s adventure has just begun!

programme.title: Monster Hunt
programme.desc: The pregnant queen of the monster realm flees a civil war and lands in human world, near Yung Ning Village. She seeks the help of a wimpy villager to become the surrogate father for her child, Wuba. From the time he was born, little Wuba embarks on a thrilling journey to escape from those who want to capture him at all costs.

programme.title: Miracles of The Namiya General Store, The
programme.desc: From Japan's best-selling author, Keigo Higashino, comes a heartwarming fantasy of an everyday general store that becomes a portal through time. When three delinquents accidentally enter the premise, they trigger a series of events that allow a letter from the past, seeking advice, to mysteriously slips through the mail slot.

programme.title: Young Heroes of Chaotic Times
programme.desc: This story is set in Shanghai in the late Qing Dynasty, and talks about a young man, Chen Zhen, who rises to become a national hero after enduring hardships and overcoming challenges in life.

programme.title: My Darling Genie
programme.desc: A genie who is trapped in a Chinese oil umbrella helps an honorable young man and his uncle to deal with a covetous loan shark.

programme.title: Caught in Time
programme.desc: Based on true events, Detective Zhong Cheng leads a task force in pursuit of Eagle, a criminal gang led by Zhang Sun. Highly methodical and disciplined, the gang manages to avoid capture after each heist. A decade later, the need to stop Eagle is more urgent than ever when Zhong Cheng realizes that his time is almost up to solve the case.

programme.title: HK Lan Kwai Fong
programme.desc: Lee is the Production head of an advertising firm who tries to improve her team’s performance by competing with Creative head Chan in the day and clubbing at Lan Kwai Fong for ideas at night. Lee runs into her ex-boyfriend before a big commercial shoot and drowns her sorrows drinking at Lan Kwai Fong, but finally picks herself up with Chan’s help.

programme.title: Men From The Monastery
programme.desc: At the end of the Ming Dynasty, Wu San Gui betrays his people to the Qing officials and recruits fighters from all backgrounds. Members from Wudan and Ermei are the first to yield and collude with local bullies. When they start attacking the Shaolin Monastery, its most famous disciples have to band together and fight against the enemies.

programme.title: A Maid From Heaven
programme.desc: The seventh daughter of the Jade Emperor is banished from heaven to live a mortal life as she is very mischievous. She falls in love with a young village lad Yong, who sold himself to work for the rich so as to bury his father. The goddess sisters help Yong to pay his debt so the lovebirds can be together. Is this going to end happily-ever-after?

programme.title: The Fantastic Magic Baby
programme.desc: The story is about the legendary Monkey King (Liu Chung-chun) teams up with Goddess of Mercy (Chao Li-chuan) and the Dragon Girl (Lung Nu) to battle the child god Hung Hai-erh (Ting Hua-chung),son of the Ox Demon (Hung Hai-erh) to rescue Tang Tseng, the Holy Pilgrim (Teng Chio-jen).

programme.title: Hong Kong 73
programme.desc: In 1973, the Hong Kong Heng Seng Index hit extraordinary peaks and people from all walks of life go stock market crazy. Meanwhile, Hong Kong's social problems build up without anyone paying attention to what are actually happening to the crazy lives of people, in this mad city that many call home...

programme.title: The Golden Sword
programme.desc: Swordswoman supreme Cheng Pei-pei (Crouching Tiger, Hidden Dragon) teams up with director/writer/actor Lo Wei (director of Bruce Lee and Jackie Chan’s first major movies) for an evocative and terrific “Martial arts world” adventure consisting of a missing blade and a deadly sect of men-hating swordswomen.

programme.title: The Butterfly Chalice
programme.desc: Starring the stunning, teenage heartthrob Pat Ting Hung, The Butterfly Chalice marks the important directing debut of the kung-fu film genre's most principle figure Chang Cheh, as he burst the martial arts and swordplay movie doors wide open, announcing the beginning of the end for the Cantonese musicals.

programme.title: The 36Th Chamber Of Shaolin
programme.desc: Gordon Liu plays an anti-Manchu rebel who escapes to the Shaolin Temple and learns what it truly takes to become a martial arts master by challenging the 35 Shaolin Kung Fu chambers, eventually creating the 36th chamber himself.

programme.title: Mist Over Dream Lake
programme.desc: A young girl Chen is sent away by her parents who are going through divorce, to stay with the Changs. On the Chang’s farm, she meets their daughter Ling Yun, the eldest son Ling Hsiao, and a young artist Hsu, and spends a summer with them that she will never forget.

programme.title: Shaolin Temple
programme.desc: As more people are learning martial arts from Shaolin, the Qing court orders for it to be banned and plans to destroy the temple. The Shaolin disciples decide to take their protest to the streets, using Shaolin skills to curb their hatred, but when the Qing troops start attacking Shaolin Temple, the disciples vow to protect it at all costs.

programme.title: The 5 Billion Dollar Legacy
programme.desc: A crippled billionaire mails a letter to each of his long-lost daughters inviting them to go to Japan, in the hope that he will find a worthy heir to inherit his vast fortune. The sisters finally meet abroad the plane to Japan, and one of them is taken with a man who is going to investigate the death of his lawyer uncle in a mysterious hit-and-run.

programme.title: Torrent Of Desire
programme.desc: Rich playboy David is a drunk until he falls in love with a fashion model Dan Feng and marries her. David's sister Mona is in love with his best friend Han Ming, who rejected her as he secretly loves Dan Feng as well. Out of jealousy and hatred, Mona lies to David about a fake affair between Han Ming and Dan Feng...

programme.title: The Killer Has No Return
programme.desc: Professional killer Lui goes to Malaysia after completing his mission of killing the big boss of a Hong Kong gang. His next target is a groom who is throwing his wedding banquet at a hotel in Chinatown. Just when Lui takes aim at his target, another victim instead of the groom is shot, and he becomes a scapegoat in this mystery assassination.

programme.title: Hong Kong Nocturne
programme.desc: This joyous, raucous, & colorful tunefest showcases the little seen dancing talents of celebrated kung-fu swordswoman Cheng Pei-Pei, as one of 3 girls dancing their way to the top.

programme.title: The Rescue
programme.desc: Celebrated scriptwriter Shen Chiang (Heroes of Sung) continues to spread his magic touch to directing with this tale surrounding the end of the Song dynasty. Threatened by the Yuan who are closing in to rule the whole of China, a band of Song survivors band together to save their prime minister. This bold and fearless heroes fighting for their cause are led by international star, Lo Lieh (Glass Tears, Killer Clans) and Shi Szu ( Lovers Destiny), who must fight their way out of trap after trap. But they can't escape them all, and eventually the two end up in prison... it is either death or a fight to the end!

programme.title: The Last Tempest
programme.desc: This sequel to The Empress Dowager continues the tale of Emperor Guangxu and Empress Dowager Cixi. Despite Guangxu’s enthronement, his ability to rule effectively is overshadowed by the ever-present power of Cixi. When his attempts to reform the Imperial system are thwarted by the Empress Dowager, Guangxu attempts to curb her power.

programme.title: The Delightful Forest
programme.desc: The legendary hero Wu Sung is sent to a prison in Meng province after murdering his adulterous sister-in-law and her lover. While in prison, the officer Shih En spares Wu the humiliating baton punishment. Owing Shih a favour, Wu decides to help Shih get his restaurant back at all costs when it was forcefully taken over by a local thug.

programme.title: Whose Baby Is In The Classroom?
programme.desc: Chen, a male teacher in an all girls’ high school, is stuck with a baby that isn’t his and must take care of it. As he lives on the school grounds, the baby is a source of constant distraction and worry! Luckily, his class warms to the baby and helps him take care of it while he works his charm on Li Ching, an uptight teacher in the same school.

programme.title: Little Hero
programme.desc: An orphan, Little Bastard is taken on and trained as a fighter by a hermit. When Little Bastard grows up, he feels he is old enough to go out and look for his parents. Luckily for him, he befriends a beggar, Hsiao Yi, who being street-wise, manages to help him find his family, but somehow gets into trouble with the gang.

programme.title: Till The End Of Time
programme.desc: This is Jenny Hu's stunning debut as a struggling singer who tries to keep her career and marriage intact. This movie also includes seven memorable hit songs.

programme.title: The Assassin
programme.desc: Notorious assassin Nieh Cheng has retired into hiding. However, when Premier Yen's family is massacred, he seeks out the reclusive swordsman & coaxes him into a final revenge mission in this epic story set in the Six Kingdom era.

programme.title: Princess Iron Fan
programme.desc: As Monkey (Yueh Hua) and his gang make their way to the West through Fire Mountain, they ran into the evil Princess Iron Fan (Pat Ting Hung), Madam White Bone (Cheng Pei Pei) and her sexy sister (Lily Ho), and have to fight their way through.

programme.title: The Spirit Of The Sword
programme.desc: Water Clan Chief is severely wounded by a samurai killer shortly before the annual duel at Tai Lake. He sends his brother Bao Yu on a long journey to find an antidote for him. On the way, Bao Yu encounters Little Princess and falls in love with her, not knowing that she is hiding a secret plot…

programme.title: Moonlight Serenade
programme.desc: A sweet inn-keeper’s daughter is witness to a perverted rape, leading to more danger than most romantic dramas can handle. Can her true love rescue her in time? For this movie, the moonlight serenade is the sound of suspense, leading to more danger than most romantic dramas can handle.

programme.title: Bloody Parrot
programme.desc: A swordsman is suspected of being the thief of a treasure sent to Emperor. Through his investigation, he is led on to the trail of the supernatural “Bloody Parrot”. Poisonous things happen including a demonic possession, witches casting poison spells and disgusting autopsies. Then a dead constable turns into a vampire!

programme.title: The House Of 72 Tenants
programme.desc: The 72 inhabitants of a dilapidated tenement live under the thumb of a heartless landlady and her sleazy husband. The arrival of a defiant new tenant however, changes their fate. The residents pool their resources together to prevent evictions, deflect targeted harassment by a corrupt policeman and ultimately prevent their home from being sold.

programme.title: The Singing Escort
programme.desc: Betty Ting plays Susan, a young woman hiding from her father by being a nightclub singer in Japan. Pop singer Chao Ke-jen (Lin Chong) gets permission from his boss to visit Japan, with the condition that he finds the boss's daughter. Boy finds girl, boy falls in love. But will the father approve?

programme.title: Lady With A Sword
programme.desc: Swordswoman Feng tries to find a group of villains responsible for her eldest sister's death, but is shocked to discover that her fiancé, Jin, is one of them. At the same time, Jin's mother and the two other killers are planning to kill Feng. Can Feng fight back and take her revenge?

programme.title: Puppy Love
programme.desc: To the tune of the Osmonds hit song, this is a story of adolescent playfulness & innocence lost. Two best friends grow up together and teasingly meet two delightfully impish boys leading to the four to flirtatiously intermingle. However, the innocence of partner swapping eventually leads to a roller-coaster bouts of misunderstood emotions.

programme.title: To Kill A Jaguar
programme.desc: Set in 1920s Shanghai, a village girl journeys to the big city in search of her father and meets her childhood friend Jaguar, who works for the mob boss Kam. In a world controlled by the mobs, it is a test of survival for all as Jaguar allies himself with ace gunman Ko Tang, to take over Kam’s empire.

programme.title: Carry On Doctors And Nurses
programme.desc: At St. Morant Hospital, a harried but lovely administrator must deal with lusty interns, student nurses, a delirious surgeon, a dissection fiend, a criticizing Commissioner and gross negligence at regular intervals! This comedy is based on the hugely successful British Carry On! film series.

programme.title: Swordswomen Three
programme.desc: Crouching Tiger, Hidden Dragon could be called "Swordswomen Two." Three decades earlier, Shen Yi, Essie Lin Chia, and Pan Ying-tzu took on Shaw's first international superstar, Lo Lieh for the Han Family Sword - making this a four-star treat for action fans.

programme.title: Young Lovers
programme.desc: Guitar-playing rich kid, Yang Fan, heads to Japan to join a rock 'n' roll band where he soon finds himself competing for the affections of two beautiful girls.

programme.title: Duel For Gold
programme.desc: Six swordsmen, including two sisters and their husbands, a ranger and a security man, are trying to steal a million gold taels from the Fu Lai Treasury House, not knowing that one of them is actually an undercover hero. In their quest, they have to double-cross and outwit one another...

programme.title: The Crazy Bumpkins
programme.desc: This side-splitting comedy sees naive Ah Niu headed to Hong Kong, where he is repeatedly exploited and taken advantage of, and eventually finds himself arrested and imprisoned! Can he survive difficult times and finally overcome adversity?

programme.title: Yaman
programme.desc: After losing his father to a bunch of scheming politicians, a young man decides to wade into the corrupt and unscrupulous world of politics to avenge his death.

programme.title: Kanaa
programme.desc: A woman who hails from a middle-class family background aims to excel in the competitive world of cricket with the help of her supportive father.

programme.title: Rajini Murugan
programme.desc: An unemployed Rajini Murugan falls in love with Karthika, but her father opposes their union due to an old misunderstanding. Things get better after Rajini inherits his grandfather's property.

programme.title: Idhu Kadhirvelan Kadhal
programme.desc: Kathir, who hates marriage, is in Coimbatore to resolve a family dispute. There, he falls for Pavithra but his heart is broken when he discovers that she is in love with someone else.

programme.title: Irumbuthirai
programme.desc: A military officer borrows money from a bank using fake papers for his sister's marriage. However, when the money goes missing from his account, he begins an investigation that leads him to a hacker.

programme.title: Blood Money
programme.desc: 2 brothers from India working in Kuwait are sentenced to death penalty for killing an srilankan women. Day before there hanging the news breakout in an Indian news channel by a lady reporter.

programme.title: Thunder
programme.desc: After CBI officer Bose recovers from a coma, people start to address him by a different name. However, he soon realises that this is a plot by the state CM to seek revenge for an old rivalry. How Bose rediscovers his past and identity forms the rest of the story.

programme.title: Enai Noki Payum Thotta
programme.desc: Raghu, a normal college guy gets dragged into trouble when he falls in love with Lekha and their whirlwind romance changes the course of his life.

programme.title: India Pakistan
programme.desc: Two aspiring lawyers, Karthick and Mellina, not knowing that both are of the same profession, share an office due to financial problems. Things take a turn when they work on the same case.

programme.title: 6 Candles
programme.desc: A father travels across six states to try and solve the mystery of his son's disappearance.

programme.title: Bhajrangi 2
programme.desc: Araka, a cruel drug baron, kidnaps innocent villagers and forces them to work for him. But, when Bhajarangi, a forest officer, learns about this, he decides to come to the villagers' rescue.

programme.title: Kaadan
programme.desc: Kaadan is a true-blue animal film signifying a deep and strong bond between humans and animals.

programme.title: Soodhu Kavvum
programme.desc: Das, with his team, kidnap Arumai, son of a politician, who has been planning his own kidnapping to extract money from his father. Problems arise, when an insane cop is brought to handle the case.

programme.title: F3
programme.desc: Venky, a middle-class businessman, his friend Varun, an orphan, Tamanna, her sister Mehreen and Raghu, a failed producer, team up with Rajendra Prasad, an honest cop fed up with his corrupt boss Commissioner Sampath, for a heist.

programme.title: Mirugaa
programme.desc: Forest officials in Kotagiri hunt a man-eating tiger that is attacking innocent people. At the same time, a serial killer is on the prowl for wealthy single women.

programme.title: Vanamagan
programme.desc: Kavya, a rich girl, goes to a restricted area in Andaman to celebrate the New Year with her friends. While evading the forest officers in the jungle, she knocks Jara, a tribal man, with her car.

programme.title: Sivalinga
programme.desc: Raheem gets killed when he tries to save a blind man in a train. When the police close the case stating suicide, Raheem's girlfriend asks Shivalingeshwaran, a CID officer, to investigate the death.

programme.title: Adhe Kangal
programme.desc: Varun Murali, a blind chef and owner of a restaurant, falls in love with his customer Deepa. However, his life takes an unusual turn after he realises the truth about her.

programme.title: Vetrivel
programme.desc: In a bid to help his younger brother unite with the girl he loves, Vetrivel and his friends decide to kidnap her. Things take an ugly turn when their plan goes wrong and results in messy situations

programme.title: Balle Vellayatheva
programme.desc: Sakthi moves to a new village after his mother, who is a postmaster, gets transferred. He befriends a childless couple and falls in love with Thanikodi, a butcher's daughter.

programme.title: Miss India
programme.desc: After moving to the USA, an aspiring Indian entrepreneur is forced to deal with sexism, criticism and rivalry as she attempts to start her tea business.

programme.title: Kavan
programme.desc: A TV journalist goes against the orders of his corrupt and dishonest boss and helps a group of youngsters in their fight against a pesticide factory.

programme.title: Raa Raa The Noisy Lion Ep22

programme.title: Postman Pat Delivery Service Ep21
programme.desc: Postman Pat And The Space Suit - It's a snowy day in Greendale, and Ted Glen has invited the kids to his workshop to meet his friend, space expert Professor Farrow. Julian's excited but so is Pat, who has always yearned to be an astronaut. He's even more thrilled when he finds that his special delivery is a space suit - an extra surprise for the kids. When his van breaks down in a snowy lane, he finds an ingenious solution - only to suffer a puncture - and Ted is unable to help... Meanwhile, Professor Farrow and Lauren take the kids out into the snow and re-create the surface of the moon. Pat's determined to make his delivery, but how will he make it on foot through the snow? As the kids perfect their snowy “moon”, a space-suited figure approaches - Pat in the space suit. Mission Accomplished!

programme.title: Postman Pat Delivery Service Ep22
programme.desc: Postman Pat And The Stormy Birthday - It's Chris Beacon's birthday and he's looking forward to spending the day onshore and having a party at the village hall. Pat's SDS mission is to pick up all the presents from everyone who won't be able to be at the party later. The kids and Lauren are working on decorating the village hall and making Ben a big card from them all whilst Nisha and Ajay provide special birthday cakes for Chris and Micawber and Alf and Dorothy send over lovely fresh eggs and cheese and a special homemade woolly jumper. Meanwhile, the weather is getting worse out at Pencaster Lighthouse and Chris realises, sadly, that he'll have to stay and man the lighthouse and make sure that the passing boats are protected. He won't be able to join everyone for his birthday after all! But Pat has a great idea – if Chris can't come to the birthday party, the birthday party can come to him! With the help of the SDS helicopter Pat delivers all of Chris's birthday presents directly to him at the lighthouse! Everyone contacts Chris by video conference so that even if they can't be there, he's not alone on his birthday! Special delivery service – mission accomplished!

programme.title: Captain Underpants Special 2 - Mega Blissmas Ep1
programme.desc: Captain Underpants And The Xtreme Xploits Of The Xplosive Xmas Special - George and Harold love Christmas, but they feel like it could use some upgrades. So they make a comic about a new version of the holiday: BLISSMAS. Instead of red bows, laser shows! Instead of ugly sweaters, cool capes! Instead of decorating trees, creating tree-bots! The boys take Melvin’s time toad back to convince Santa to incorporate some of their ideas to his new holiday. But they come back to the present to find that their plan didn’t work quite how they’d hoped. George and Harold realize they need to help Santa remember the true meaning of Christmas before it’s gone forever!

programme.title: Dragons Rescue Riders S1 Ep20

programme.title: Tinga Tinga Tales Ep13
programme.desc: Why Vulture Is Bald - You see there was time when Vulture was not bald. Oh no, Vulture's head was covered in a beautiful crown of golden plumage! Vain Vulture never shut up about her golden feathers and was obsessed about making them ‘as golden as the sun!'. One day Vulture decides to fly up to the sun, but her precious feathers get burnt! Vulture decides to sooth her smoking feathers with golden honey which she steals from the bees. The bees are not pleased and Vulture sticks her head down Aardvark's burrow. However, Aardvark loves feathers all covered in honey and when Vulture surfaces she is as bald as… well, as a Vulture! Tales from Africa.

programme.title: Tinga Tinga Tales Ep14
programme.desc: Why Giraffe Has A Long Neck - You see there was a time when Giraffe didn't have a long neck. Her neck was all short and stumpy and she was a very delicate eater. All the food in Tinga Tinga seemed to make her tummy go funny. Then one day Lion suggests she try some honey. With the Bees permission, Giraffe tries to lick the honey… but it is deep, deep inside the tree. Giraffe squeezes her head into the honey tree and then EEEeeek! Her head gets stuck! Summer, Autumn, Winter pass by with Giraffe's head stuck inside the tree, but she is quite happy because the honey is so delicious. The tree grows and Giraffe's neck gets longer and longer! After a whole year ‘POP!' she manages to pull herself free and from that day on Giraffe has a very long neck and can eat the freshest leaves on the very tops of the trees! Tales from Africa.

programme.title: Noddy Toyland Detective Ep13
programme.desc: The Case Of The Sticky Putty - Something very strange is happening in Brickabuild. Clockwork Mouse is giving all sorts of confusing orders to the builders and everything is chaos. Noddy realises that someone has put sticky putty on her clockwork key and it's making her run slowly. Noddy decides to investigate and find out who could have tried to damage the little mouse. Following all the clues and keeping track of all the evidence in his WhoWhatWhere Tablet, Noddy finds that the trail leads him to Carlton! But Carlton adores Clockwork Mouse! Noddy discovers that poor Carlton didn't meant to damage her; he just wanted to help her rest and not work so hard. Noddy has a brilliant idea. If Clockwork Mouse and Carlton work together, they can get all their jobs finished in half the time. And then there'll be plenty of time to rest – and play! Good idea Noddy!

programme.title: Noddy Toyland Detective Ep14
programme.desc: The Case Of The Toyland Accidents - Something strange is happening in Toyland – trees are falling down and machines are going crazy. What's going on? Noddy needs to use all his investigating skills to find out who is causing all the accidents before someone gets hurt. He realises that Deltoid is trying to help and be a superhero but hasn't realised that his superstrength is causing chaos! Noddy shows him how to be a super helpful superhero without causing anymore accidents! Well done Noddy!

programme.title: Guess With Jess Ep13
programme.desc: Why Do Bees Make Honey? - Mimi's munching some honey sandwiches at the Hutch when Jess comes to visit. She shows him the lovely pots of honey she has and he wonders why bees need to make it. He thinks maybe Jess wonders if it might be used as glue but when Horace singing him a groovy song about HOW honey is made, Jess has an idea that it might be used as food during the winter when there's no pollen..

programme.title: Guess With Jess Ep14

Making his debut in the Sunshine State, South Carolina’s Thompson is one of the elite strikers in the UFC, but that’s just the kind of fight Texas’ Holland craves, setting the stage for a memorable night in the Octagon’s return to Florida. Plus, top five heavyweights go head-to-head as Australian knockout artist Tai Tuivasa looks to stop the surging Sergei Pavlovich, who is riding the momentum of four straight victories in the Octagon
